{"tid":15182,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美少女飲麻油雞湯醉咗 甜笑萌態迷倒網友","createTime":"2016-12-01T01:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T10:15:19.000Z","uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e06fd75512ec5d3d77a2c8859d21e7a3eebe7457","tid":15182,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:09:29.000Z","msg":"美少女飲麻油雞湯醉咗 甜笑萌態迷倒網友<br />\n<br />\n喝麻油雞湯也會醉？台灣有女網民前日在facebook貼出兩段影片，出賣妹妹的醉態，笑稱是「最正ㄎㄧㄤ（有指人沒喝酒卻處在酒醉狀之意）妹」，原來妹妹喝了幾碗媽媽煮的麻油雞湯就醉了，不但臉紅，還靠在椅上一直傻笑，不時擺出蓮花指直呼：「我沒有醉！」讓全家人都笑歪。影片隨後被瘋傳，引發超過2萬人讚她笑容好甜：「戀愛了」，紛紛跪求fb。<br />\n<br />\n女網民日前將這兩段影片po上facebook「爆廢公社」，笑說：「我家的87妹喝麻油雞湯也可以醉，最正ㄎ一ㄤ妹，笑死！」影片中，只見留着一頭飄逸長髮的妹妹靠坐在椅子上，一臉通紅不斷傻笑，媽媽還神配音一句：「阿娘威，喝麻油雞也會醉安捏厲害內！」妹妹則微醺一直嚷着：「我沒有醉啦！」還添了半碗湯繼續喝，一度還唱起歌。<br />\n<br />\n一旁拍攝的姊姊看着妹妹手勢，直問「你的手在幹嘛？」姊妹倆笑成一團，連爸爸都笑說：「她有沒有醉，看她有沒有蓮花指就知道。」還附上一張妹妹整個醉躺在地板上玩手機的照片，讓人看了也惹不住嘴角失守。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161201/55985001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161201%2F55985001&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUinvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f693b943\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161201%2F55985001&h=ee1d5804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161201/55985001</a>"},{"pid":"f2ba0bf39bb787f48abc6e72f7ee0599ccce954c","tid":15182,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c03c531a40ed9e2299219b9c42d4ee7d7173d088","tid":15182,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想要妹妹"},{"pid":"010053d5fe3c38ac53ed2cb2888b50304cafd4cb","tid":15182,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"Lm一陣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda048f80c64cc21ef1753125b7b37fe7275be59","tid":15182,"uid":42090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"戀愛了"},{"pid":"f8c3bdaf25c94aabb335abd128262e67e3061253","tid":15182,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:31:14.000Z","msg":"哥也是醉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afd36b6b5840eae5e0377677da8640041dd9ce2","tid":15182,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"麻友雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真的戀愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1465cc5a44616b90f0376c843a3e06b7dcb94f7e","tid":15182,"uid":2567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"Reported"},{"pid":"d57f0480cc7d581a2f356e004b6b8d621d59c225","tid":15182,"uid":35891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11876d7dcfcafd1be55a3c3060e3066437dced42","tid":15182,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511532e7e83f8465d41faeff9bb4bac130883351","tid":15182,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:09:04.000Z","msg":"麻友g"},{"pid":"76e5b863fa443a2ac2c8c7dc57db4a10e36817a0","tid":15182,"uid":34852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f267db64e000ef59593220a5ef15a10ad9172e","tid":15182,"uid":38189,"li